description:
Precious thrown away,
Here abound to unfold and melt. 
I'm only where the sound
is shaking at the lips of the well felt.
And where are your eyes? 
And where are your eyes? 
Slip through the sky carefully they’re cut. 
And where is your heart?
And where is your heart?
Elite powerfully burn to keep it shut. .
.
.
.
.
